me in third place.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2216, \"end\": 2223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvians\", \"score\": 0.9978173901067638, \"rank\": 0.0021873618446265216, \"text\": \"Latvian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Second place\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"the BelgianEdgard Collecame\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"third place\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were given silver-plated medals and the rest of the finalists were awarded bronze medals.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver-plated medals\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"the finalists\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze medals\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ireland finished in 15th position with O'Hanlon winning 5\\u00bd points.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9998197695648463, \"rank\": 0.00018026279511017772, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2424, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00d3_hAnluain\", \"score\": 0.6638756586635746, \"rank\": 0.48484848484842324, \"text\": \"O'Hanlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00d3_hAnluain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00d3_hAnluain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"15th position\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chess has a long history in Ireland with the ancient board game of fidchel